c: 7
v: 172
t: "Unibuke ubwo Nyagasani wawe yazanaga (roho zose za) bene Adamu n’iz’urubyaro ruzaturuka mu migongo yabo, maze akazishyira imbere ye akazibwira ati \"Ese si njye Nyagasani wanyu? Baravuga bati \"Nibyo, turahamya ko uri Nyagasani wacu\". ( Allah aravuga ati, ibi mbikoze) kugira ngo ku munsi w’imperuka mutazavuga muti \"Mu by’ukuri, ibi ntitwabimenye"